Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl

Class SubstationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.SubstationService
  • public final class SubstationService
extends Object
    A representation of the SubstationService.

    The following features are supported:

    • Adds the Substation object from given SCL object
    • Adds the TVoltageLevel element under TSubstation reference object
    • Adds the TBay element under TVoltageLevel reference object
    • Update the value of LNode@iedName attribute corresponding to the value of ICDHeader@IEDName attribute
    See Also:
    SubstationAdapter, VoltageLevelAdapter, BayAdapter, FunctionAdapter, LNodeAdapter, PrivateService

      • updateLNodeIEDNames

        public static void updateLNodeIEDNames​(SCL scd)
                                throws ScdException
        Updates all LNodes IEDNames in given SCD file
        • If LNode contents one Private Compas-ICDHEADER so LNode name is update with IED name from the Private
        • If LNode contents more than one Private Compas-ICDHEADER so new LNodes are created for each Private Compas-ICDHEADER and naming them with the Private IED name
        Parameters:
        scd - SCL file in which LNodes names should be updated
        Throws:
        ScdException - throws when no Private Compas-ICDHEADER found on at least one LNode of current SCL file
